            . I am a <rs id="t18200918-213-viclabel1231" type="occupation">shoemaker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-213-victim2090 t18200918-213-viclabel1231"></join>. The prisoner was my <rs id="t18200918-213-deflabel1232" type="occupation">journeyman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-213-defend2088 t18200918-213-deflabel1232"></join>. I missed a pair of upper leathers, and found them at Wenston's. He said he had them from Robinson, and, in consequence of what Robinson said, I took the prisoner and told him. Robinson said he had the pair of upper leathers from Sadler - he said nothing. Sadler was convicted of receiving them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200918-213-person2092">
